<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1087337-why-did-jonathan-ferris-and-sienna-brooks">Why did Jonathan Ferris and Sienna Brooks have exactly the same encounter with Zobrist? I was confused by this.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1087337'><a id="like_count_community_question_1087337" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1087337?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">12 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F17212231-inferno">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1087337-why-did-jonathan-ferris-and-sienna-brooks">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1087337-why-did-jonathan-ferris-and-sienna-brooks">See all 8 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/5967346-mark-b-epstein"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_100x100-c7bfe730633c9983e27caaa66a8e244a.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/5967346-mark-b-epstein">Mark B. Epstein</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Initially I was confused as well. At first, you are led to believe that Ferris is FS-2080. So when you read about FS-2080's first encounter with Zobri<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Initially I was confused as well. At first, you are led to believe that Ferris is FS-2080. So when you read about FS-2080's first encounter with Zobrist, you think that it is Ferris who is thinking about the encounter. It's not until later in the story that you learn that FS-2080 is really Sienna Brooks. I actually went back and re-read the initial encounter as it was first described while the three (Ferris, Brooks &amp; Langdon) are on the train. It's well done. FS-2080 is never identified as male or female, nor by any other name but FS-2080. Once I read it again, after learning that FS-2080 was actually Sienna Brooks, I realized the misleading tactic and that the scene actually was being recalled by Sienna Brooks all along.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
</div>
</div>
